        <p>The <a href="http://agilehumanities.ca/"><strong>Agile Humanities Agency</strong></a> is a firm based in Toronto whose members have extensive experience with Digital Humanities development, with particular expertise in digital editions. AH helped us develop a more professional look for our website and think through the interactivity of our edition reader and variorum interfaces. We also worked with them to resolve some of our unique navigation needs.</p>

